events.name: Miami Hurricanes at North Carolina Tar Heels

headlines.description: — After a huge first half, RJ Davis saw no reason to back off.
headlines.shortLinkText: Davis sets Smith Center record with 42 points as No. 9 North Carolina beats Miami 75-71

events.name: Baylor Bears at TCU Horned Frogs

headlines.description: — Standout freshman Ja'Kobe Walter started a game-turning spurt for 15th-ranked Baylor with a slam dunk and ended it by blowing a kiss to the TCU student section after making a 3-pointer.
headlines.shortLinkText: Baylor freshman Ja'Kobe Walter big after halftime as No. 15 Bears beat TCU 62-54
